
<section id="trending_media">
  <center><h2>Trending Now</h2></center>
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <% @trending_media.in_groups_of(3).each do |group| %>
    <div class="row">
      <% group.each do |media| %>
        <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div id="media_<%= media.id %>">
          <h3><%= media.title %></h3>
          <img src=<%="https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500#{media.poster_path}"%>>
          <div class="lead">
            <p>Vote Average: <%= media.round_vote %></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
      <% end %>
  </div>
</section>

<div id="about_us">
  <center><h2>Who Are We?</h2></center>
  <div class="lead">
    <p>StreamLined is your new go-to media tracking tool that enables users to organize their movie and TV show watching activity. Upon signing up for the application, users access a user-friendly dashboard with three default lists to categorize their media: 'Currently Watching,' 'Want to Watch,' and 'Watched.' The intuitive interface allows users to search for their desired media titles, view essential details, and save them to the appropriate list effortlessly.</p>
    <p>StreamLined is the perfect tool for busy individuals who want to keep track of their favorite movies and TV shows with ease. Its simple interface and practical features make it an essential addition to any media lover's toolkit.</p>
    <p>If you enjoy StreamLined, check out the source code on <%= link_to 'Github', 'https://github.com/Streamlined-Turing/streamlined_fe' %></p>
  </div>
</div>
